HB 215 Draft 2026 Regular Session Robby Carter
Abstract: Changes the max property value that qualifies for a small succession.
Present law (C.C.P. Art. 3421(1)) provides that a small succession is the succession of a
person domiciled in the state of La. leaving property with a gross value of $125,000 or less.
